Game information:

Imagine a world where your every action will not remain without
consequences and necessarily affect your future destiny. A world
where every step you will vary subtly, gradually turning into a
valiant warrior, fighting evil ... or in a decrepit mage with black
thoughts. The whole world - only a series of tests by which everything
will be able to behold your true nature.
Be a hero. Be a traitor. Be yourself.
